---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About Us | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="page-layout">
			<h1>About WKND Harvest</h1>
			<p class="lead">We curate the stories that matter — from the corners of the internet you don't have time to check.</p>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>What We Do</h2>
				<p>WKND Harvest is a digital magazine for the globally curious. We cover AI & Tech, Shopping, Travel, Health, Family, Sports, and Lifestyle — but we don't just report the news. We find the angle that makes you think differently.</p>
				<p>Every story is chosen because it answers a question worth asking: Why is this happening? What does it mean for you? Where is the opportunity?</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>Our Story</h2>
				<p>WKND Harvest was built by people who live between cultures, languages, and time zones. We speak Arabic, French, English, and Spanish — and we use that access to pull stories from sources most English-only publications miss.</p>
				<p>We started because we were tired of algorithm-driven content farms and clickbait. We wanted something with a pulse. Something that respects your intelligence.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>How We Work</h2>
				<p>We publish daily across all sections. Our editorial process is simple: if we wouldn't share it with a friend over coffee, it doesn't make the cut.</p>
				<p>We use AI as a research tool, not a writer. Every article is edited by humans who care about accuracy, clarity, and voice.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="about-section">
				<h2>Contact</h2>
				<p>Have a story idea? Want to collaborate? Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@wkndharvest.com">hello@wkndharvest.com</a> or visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.page-layout {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		color: #d0d0d0;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}
	.page-layout h1 {
		font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}
	.lead {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: #888;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.about-section {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	.about-section h2 {
		font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #f5c518;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}
	.about-section p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.about-section a {
		color: #f5c518;
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.about-section a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>